metadata.title: moonsix Tactical Belts for Men, Webbing Duty Military Belt with Plastic Buckle
features: Travel friendly heavy duty belt-- Non-metallic POM plastic buckle for easy, quick clearance at security checkpoints. The buckle does not contain any metal components, especially suitable for metal allergy to wear, not easy to crack and breakage. Lightweight! Airport Friendly!
This casual nylon webbing belt is not only used for daily wearing, but also a good tactical gear for outdoor sports and heavy duty work, hunting, hiking, shooting, concealed carrying.

Material: Outdoor belt makes with high quality nylon that has a strong evaporation of sweat,more comfortable and breathable. Unique modeling with concise style perfect for decorating with all kinds of clothes.

SUITABLE FOR PANT SIZE BELOW 46". Size Details of moonsix Heavy Duty Belt(approx): Total length(not included buckle):52"; The Width of the Strap:1.6";The Thickness of the Strap:0.12".The Length of the Buckle:2.4";The Width of the Buckle:1.8" (From End to end,due to manual measurement,a 1/4-1 inch's variation is considered to be normal.)
These MEN's belts can also be used by WOMEN. Weight(approx):126Gram/PC. Quantity:1x nylon belt. Comes with a attractive gift bag,make a big impression!
description: This is a high quality durable,strong nylon/elastic belt with a classic timeless design. It's suitable for almost all ages people daily wear and nice popular gift for students, youth, men, old man as father's day gift, thanksgiving day gift, Christmas Day gift. The belt is not only used for daily wearing, but also let you be more fashion and can show your own taste.Adjustable and useful, always gives you the best choice of men's fashion.
